EDUCATIONAL PURPOSE DISCLAIMER:

This repository contains intentionally vulnerable code examples for educational 
purposes only. The vulnerable code patterns demonstrated here should NEVER be 
used in production environments. 

The authors and contributors of this repository:
- Are not responsible for any misuse of the information provided
- Do not encourage or condone the use of these techniques for malicious purposes
- Strongly recommend thorough security audits before deploying any Solana program
- Provide this content solely for educational and security research purposes

By using this repository, you acknowledge that:
- You understand the educational nature of this content
- You will not use vulnerable patterns in production code
- You will use this knowledge to improve security, not to cause harm
- You are responsible for ensuring your own code follows security best practices

Always conduct comprehensive security reviews and testing before deploying any 
blockchain application to mainnet.